---
title: Sarh — Property approval (1/3) · Submission + Officer review + Manager approval
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Citizen
    actor O as Registry officer
    actor M as Department<br/>Manager
    participant W as apps/web (Angular)
    participant API as .NET 8 API
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Note over C,DB: 1) Submission
    C->>W: fill form + draw polygon
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties { polygon, area, docs }
    API->>DB: INSERT properties (status='pending')
    API->>DB: INSERT registration_requests
    DB-->>API: property_id, request_no
    API-->>W: 201 SubmitResult

    Note over O,DB: 2) Officer review (technical + spatial)
    O->>W: open /app/queue
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/properties?status=pending
    API->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>W: list
    O->>W: open detail, read docs, view map, run conflict check
    O->>W: click "Recommend approval" + technical note
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties/:id/review { decision: 'recommend_approval' }
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='under_review',<br/>reviewed_by_officer_id
    DB->>DB: AFTER UPDATE trigger → audit_log INSERT

    Note over M,DB: 3) Department Manager final approval
    M->>W: open /app/approvals
    W->>API: GET /api/v1/properties?status=under_review
    API->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>W: list
    M->>W: review officer recommendation + decree no
    M->>W: click "Final approve"
    W->>API: POST /api/v1/properties/:id/final-approve { approval_decree_no }
    API->>DB: UPDATE properties SET status='approved',<br/>approved_by_manager_id, approval_decree_no
    DB->>DB: audit_log INSERT